<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>College Migration - Application Submitted to School</title>
</head>
<body style="
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #408e49;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
">
    <div style="
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 24px;
    ">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <div style="width: 100%; margin: 0 auto 40px">
            <img
            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ds5nnf5hi/image/upload/v1740830241/college_ilqfhe.png"
            style="width: 128px; margin: 0 auto 40px"
                alt="College Migration Logo"
            />
        </div>

        <!-- Main Image -->
        <img
            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ds5nnf5hi/image/upload/v1742678947/undraw_content_0p18_qtyb7z.png"
            style="width: 261px; margin: 0 auto 40px"
            alt="Application Submitted Illustration"
        />

        <!-- Content -->
        <h2 style="color: #1A2825; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 24px">
            Application Submitted to <%= schoolName %>
        </h2>

        <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 24px">
            <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 16px">
                Dear <%= name %>,
            </p>

            <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
                We're excited to inform you that your application has been successfully submitted to <strong><%= schoolName %></strong> for the <strong><%= programName %></strong> program.
            </p>

            <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 24px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #1A2825; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 12px;">Application Details</h3>
                <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px;"><strong>Application ID:</strong> <%= applicationId %></p>
                <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px;"><strong>Program:</strong> <%= programName %></p>
                <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px;"><strong>School:</strong> <%= schoolName %></p>
                <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 0;"><strong>Submission Date:</strong> <%= submissionDate %></p>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 24px 0 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
                The admissions team at <strong><%= schoolName %></strong> will now review your application. 
                You'll be notified as soon as there's an update regarding your application status.
            </p>

            <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 24px; line-height: 1.5;">
                If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
            </p>

            <!-- Login Button -->
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" 
                   style="
                       background-color: #408e49;
                       color: white;
                       padding: 12px 32px;
                       text-decoration: none;
                       border-radius: 8px;
                       font-weight: bold;
                       display: inline-block;
                   ">
                    View Application Status
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin: 24px 0 0;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The College Migration Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="margin: 40px -20px 0; padding: 24px 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 8px;">
                Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> College Migration. All rights reserved.
            </p>
            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">
                This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
